trans-unit.source: Performance Profiler
trans-unit.target: Performance Profiler

trans-unit.source:
<div class="preview-tabs--block preview-tabs--text">
The CPU Usage tool in the Performance Profiler (available via ALT-F2 or from the Debug menu) now automatically displays the "hot path" indicator (red flame) when displaying the Call Tree.
trans-unit.target:
<div class="preview-tabs--block preview-tabs--text">
The CPU Usage tool in the Performance Profiler (available via ALT-F2 or from the Debug menu) now automatically displays the "hot path" indicator (red flame) when displaying the Call Tree.

trans-unit.source: This saves a click on common CPU Usage performance investigations.
trans-unit.target: This saves a click on common CPU Usage performance investigations.

trans-unit.source: The Performance Profiler now participates in forward/backward navigation in the Visual Studio IDE.
trans-unit.target: The Performance Profiler now participates in forward/backward navigation in the Visual Studio IDE.

trans-unit.source: As one navigates to various views of tools in the Performance Profiler (available via ALT-F2 or from the Debug menu), navigation points are saved along with other navigation items. One can employ them by clicking the navigation buttons in Visual Studio or invoking the Visual Studio navigation commands.
trans-unit.target: As one navigates to various views of tools in the Performance Profiler (available via ALT-F2 or from the Debug menu), navigation points are saved along with other navigation items. One can employ them by clicking the navigation buttons in Visual Studio or invoking the Visual Studio navigation commands.

trans-unit.source: What is a Preview?
trans-unit.target: What is a Preview?

trans-unit.source: Visual Studio Preview gives you early access to the latest features and improvements not yet available in the main release.
trans-unit.target: Visual Studio Preview gives you early access to the latest features and improvements not yet available in the main release.

trans-unit.source: By trying Preview, you can take advantage of new builds and updates that ship on a frequent cadence.
trans-unit.target: By trying Preview, you can take advantage of new builds and updates that ship on a frequent cadence.

trans-unit.source: For more information on Visual Studio Preview installs, visit our FAQ page.
trans-unit.target: For more information on Visual Studio Preview installs, visit our FAQ page.

trans-unit.source: Please note that the preview version is continuously evolving and certain features may not work as expected.
trans-unit.target: Please note that the preview version is continuously evolving and certain features may not work as expected.

trans-unit.source: This version is also not licensed to build shipping applications.
trans-unit.target: This version is also not licensed to build shipping applications.

trans-unit.source: If you would like to build production application you can access stable release of Visual Studio from our downloads page.
trans-unit.target: If you would like to build production application you can access stable release of Visual Studio from our downloads page.
